<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:13:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴西加入竞争以放松中国对稀土行业的控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</link><description>随着西方经济体努力获取用于绿色能源和国防的磁铁所需的金属，并打破中国在供应链中的主导地位，矿业巨头巴西雄心勃勃地建立稀土行业。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 08:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazil-joins-race-loosen-chinas-grip-rare-earths-industry-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国对原产于欧盟的进口猪肉及副产品启动反倾销立案调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，已对来自欧盟的进口猪肉及其副产品启动反倾销调查，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收反补贴税后，紧张局势升级。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-opens-anti-dumping-probe-into-imported-pork-by-products-eu-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>韩国将于周二与中国举行首轮会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-korea-hold-first-round-talks-with-china-tues-2024-06-17/</link><description>首尔外交部周一表示，根据两国上个月达成的协议，韩国和中国将于周二举行第一轮外交和安全对话。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 07:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/south-korea-hold-first-round-talks-with-china-tues-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典 Essity 上调维达出售后利润率目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swedens-essity-raises-margin-target-after-vinda-sale-2024-06-17/</link><description>瑞典卫生用品制造商Essity周一上调了核心利润率目标，并重申了撤资香港上市子公司维达（3331.HK）后的核心销售目标。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 06:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swedens-essity-raises-margin-target-after-vinda-sale-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>杰富瑞表示，中国零跑汽车开始在 Stellantis 波兰工厂生产电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-started-ev-production-stellantis-polish-plant-jefferies-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>杰富瑞分析师援引零跑汽车管理层的话说，由Stellantis牵头的合资企业已开始在Stellantis位于波兰蒂黑的工厂生产中国零跑汽车的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-leapmotor-started-ev-production-stellantis-polish-plant-jefferies-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>VDMA称德国机器人行业面临来自中国的激烈竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/german-robotics-industry-faces-stiff-competition-china-vdma-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>VDMA工程协会的一位代表告诉路透社，来自中国日益激烈的竞争正在给德国机器人行业的前景带来压力，德国机器人行业已经在国内经济疲软的情况下陷入订单下降的困境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:36:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/german-robotics-industry-faces-stiff-competition-china-vdma-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>早申：法国队自摆乌龙，中国队未能欢呼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-17/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>报告称美国核电落后中国15年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-many-15-years-behind-china-nuclear-power-report-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一的一份报告称，美国在发展高科技核电方面落后中国多达 15 年，因为北京政府支持的技术方法和广泛的融资使其具有优势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 04:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-many-15-years-behind-china-nuclear-power-report-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>国防部长称台湾不寻求与中国开战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>台湾国防部长顾维钧周一表示，台湾并不寻求与北京开战，其政策是建立防御性、多层次的威慑能力，使中国更难占领该岛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂产出令人失望，房地产业陷入低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国5月份工业产出低于预期，尽管有政策支持，但房地产行业的放缓并未显示出缓解的迹象，这加大了北京提振经济增长的压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国新房价格跌幅创近10年来最快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，5月份中国新房价格跌幅为逾9-1/2年来最快，尽管政府努力遏制供应过剩并支持负债累累的开发商，但房地产行业仍在努力寻找底部。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>1-5月中国房地产投资下滑加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</link><description>尽管政策制定者加倍努力支持陷入困境的行业和提振消费者信心，但中国的房地产投资在 1 月至 4 月下降 9.8% 后，2024 年前 5 个月仍同比下降 10.1%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行维持关键政策利率不变符合预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国央行周一在到期中期贷款展期时，如预期维持关键政策利率不变，并从银行体系抽走部分资金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美元保持坚挺，政治不确定性削弱欧元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>美元周一坚挺，而欧元则交投于一个多月低点附近，因欧洲政治动荡加剧了交易员的不确定性，而投资者则等待更多数据来衡量美国经济的实力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>悲观的中国数据抵消了需求希望，油价稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一，中国经济数据凸显全球最大原油进口国的复苏之路坎坷，抵消了北半球夏季驾车季节需求提振的希望，油价保持稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 00:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>